And so, we think that the long-term strength of international pricing relative to U.S. gas is going to be pretty interesting. And that driver and that strength in LNG, we think, it's going to be driven by its role in energy transition and reducing carbon emissions. So, as you see us build out our LNG portfolio over the next few years, we may take some longer-term contract decisions in there.

